Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:13.29,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3\NThe Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. William...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Mr. William?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's this month's stock list.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, regarding the goods that\Nhave yet to arrive by sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we inquire about them\Nonce more, just in case?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I'll leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a visitor at the door...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you rode here on an elephant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at any rate, why the surprise visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother's been\Ngiving me a hard time at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you just feel like\Ntaking a trip by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"By yourself," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always came to visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd return the favor\Nand come to visit you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, let me introduce you.\NThis is my friend from lndia, Hakim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm William's sister, Grace.\NHe's told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for always looking after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm the one who was\Nalways looking after him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so exotic and handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's a friend of brother Will's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I never expected to see\Na sight like this here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like the elephants, I'll give you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose whichever one you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but no thanks.\NBesides, can those creatures be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something that large\Nwas to go on a rampage...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elephants are really quite calm and docile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare for them to attack a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very clever, sacred creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then perhaps you'd be able to\Nexplain what's happening outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about him.\NHe's just a bit cranky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I plan to stay for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since I'd like to keep things quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please don't tell anyone else that I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A member of the lndian royal family,\Nthe son of Atawari, Hakim Atawari..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...is staying with the Jones family in secret."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it's in the newspaper,\Nit's not much of a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,India, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Jones family is involved in trade.\NIt's something to do with their work, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,India...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, did he come on an elephant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unlikely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master William.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Stevens? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Hakim would like to\Nsee you in his room, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakim, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakim... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, isn't it? I can redecorate\Nyour room this way too if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks... I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do need to relax more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what did you want me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've come all this way to England,\NI thought some sightseeing would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I'll prepare a carriage for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't drank enough yet to be hallucinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has London zoo started up sightseeing trips?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Large animals like elephants should\Nuse the tube tunnels, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so conspicuous...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:09:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, huh? Even lndians\Ndon't often see this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it certainly is remarkable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't get used to the swaying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy you approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, as a special favor,\NI'll show you how fast this one can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go faster, the swaying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will just get worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful? This is my fastest elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that... can we please just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jones?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-Hakim! Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel a bit better if you throw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disgraceful, for a grown man\Nto feel ill from a simple ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People were never meant to ride such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that an elephant... would move that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I had no idea-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sweating badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that feel a bit better?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you gave me such a scare!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always drop in on people so unexpectedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll let you off the hook for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased... to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakim...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'm sorry. This is Hakim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's visiting from lndia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's fine now.\NYou may return to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so bad when you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was able to meet Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is is, Hakim? You've been very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Has someone gone out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Your guest left a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakim did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hakim?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a ride home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? No, I'm fine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Hakim...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Emma...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow that carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh that's right, lndian food\Nuses many spices, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, isn't adding all those\Nspices bad for your health?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turmeric, cloves,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cardamom, coriander, cumin,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ajwain, fennel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many spices,\Nbut they're all good for your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no... Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wilbur and Hopkins Company...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have come to deliver the item you ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the completed item.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust the name is correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, b-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The order form says that I should\Ndeliver this to the Jones residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:16:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone today, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mistress will be home soon.\NPlease have a seat, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you find the taste agreeable, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I came here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, are you and William lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad. It would have\Nbeen awkward if you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,William is one of my most precious friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to betray his friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that it's sudden,\Nand that we've only just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, I don't mean to\Ncause you trouble... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't know you very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way you stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way you move,\Nand the way you speak so gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dulcet voice is beautiful as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I love your face most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you like your own face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize if I upset you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma... if you don't mind,\NI'd like to take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanted to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I just wanted to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,William.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had that gloomy look on your face\Nall night. Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I saw the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like there's a lot going on at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your famous guest with you today?
